e&value=hot03\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/ccc7b6f11eebe736_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/007xhriZly1glc22ougg7g30e50c94qx.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/ccc7b6f11eebe736_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#Baby红毯没输过#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#Baby红毯没输过#\n\n鼻姐 红毯永不拉胯[鲜花] ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/57f98863d4bf78f3_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot04\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/57f98863d4bf78f3_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/003cgbmWly1glc6nk3fsrj65sa3zoqv602.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/57f98863d4bf78f3_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#戴着皇冠的刘亦菲好像公主#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">要说娱乐圈内最贵气的女星，刘亦菲绝对算一个吧，这组花絮大片更是说明了这一点。头戴CHAUMET皇冠的刘亦菲，丝毫没有被华丽珠宝夺去全部风采，珠宝衬人，人亦衬珠宝，相互成就。放眼整个娱乐圈，怕是很难找出比她还适合戴皇冠的明星了。#戴着皇冠的刘亦菲好像公主# ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/8c4110c1c7889f93_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot05\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/8c4110c1c7889f93_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/0033ImPzly1glc4ubn9amj60u00u248902.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/8c4110c1c7889f93_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#累计收入不超6万元月份暂不预扣个税#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【国家税务总局：2021年起，#累计收入不超6万元月份暂不预扣个税#】12月4日，国家税务总局发文优化个人所得税预扣预缴：2021年1月1日起，对上一完整纳税年度内每月均在同一单位预扣预缴工资、薪金所得个人所得税且全年工资、薪金收入不超过6万元的居民个人，扣缴义务人在预扣预缴本年度工资、薪金所得 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <div class=\"UG_box_foot\">\n        <a href=\"\/\/weibo.com\/a\/hot\/realtime\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">查看更多<i class=\"W_ficon ficon_arrow_right S_ficon\">a<\/i><\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n"})</script>
